<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer12667120709716779791">Thom Stark, author of May Day - Book One of American Sulla, has been a professional writer since 1995. He is best known as a columnist and feature writer for the late, great Boardwatch Magazine. Mr. Stark currently lives in Chillicothe, Ohio, with his wife Judy and their lovable mutts Wanda and Watson. He is hard at work on War – Book Two of American Sulla.</span>

</div>
